{"type": "article", "id": 26478, "title": "抹茶口味葡萄酒", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-06T07:08:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162602u2dqOs87p9ha40LJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个绿色的葡萄酒其实是日本商家又一次脑洞大开的产物：京都抹茶品牌<a href=\"http://www.rakuten.ne.jp/gold/itohkyuemon/ujicha_t/\">伊藤久右衛門</a>和丹波葡萄酒合作推出了一款抹茶味葡萄酒，而且还取了一个特别直白的名字叫“夜半のみどり”（みどり是绿色的意思）。它的酒精度数仅为 12%，一口饮下能同时品尝到葡萄的酸甜和抹茶微涩的后味。300 毫升装的售价为 1200 日元，你可以通过日本的<a href=\"http://item.rakuten.co.jp/itohkyuemon/c/0000000489/\">樂天市場</a>购买。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162600k0S2uAHD7OXGnq5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09411765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021626015ypcB7zMfJo3sUrb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021626010UvwXi7jSaqrORIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}